OL,4,CFamilies facing special education needs
OL,5,C'postcode lottery'
OL,6, Families seeking support for children
OL,7, with special educational needs face a
OL,8, "postcode lottery", a report suggests.
OL,10,FChildren from the poorest areas are
OL,11,Fless likely to get help than those in
OL,12,Fmore affluent areas, the Education
OL,13,FPolicy Institute (EPI) think tank says.
OL,15,FPupils have missed out on support due
OL,16,Fto remote learning and those in academy
OL,17,Fschools were less likely to be
OL,18,Fidentified as needing support, it adds.
OL,20,FThe Department for Education said the
OL,21,Fsystem needed to be more consistent.
